  <revision rev="23" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>2126074ff88766d4f5d13e44bd89b59c</srcmd5>
    <version>6.14.2</version>
    <time>1783628495</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Update to 6.14.2 (CVE-2026-59935, bsc#1271145)
  * Avoid infinite loops for incomplete ASCII85 and ASCIIHex inline
    images
  6.14.1 (CVE-2026-59936, bsc#1271146)
  * Detect end of stream during inline image end marker detection
- Update to 6.14.0 (CVE-2026-59937, bsc#1271147, CVE-2026-59938, bsc#1271148)
  * Apply general limit for requested image size
  * Speed up recovery when reading broken cross-reference table
  6.13.3
  * Apply MAX_DECLARED_STREAM_LENGTH to streams without length as well
  6.13.2
  * Detect multi-hop cyclic /Pages trees in _flatten to prevent SIGSEGV
  6.13.1 (bsc#1268787, CVE-2026-54651)
  * Prevent infinite loops when processing threads/articles</comment>
    <requestid>1364735</requestid>
  </revision>
